  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world’s weirdest factory. You don’t swing swords or cast spells, instead you build tiny heroes out of shapes, and hope for the best as they come up against endless swarms of increasingly brutal enemies. All in a day’s work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/429a6aa911900a58e8a3cda41ca0ace9.poster.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/429a6aa911900a58e8a3cda41ca0ace9.webm?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/429a6aa911900a58e8a3cda41ca0ace9.mp4?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/cbd415d756e11bf8259348c631ac8f45.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=202 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop shapes onto conveyor belts to craft self-operation heroes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a soldier? Try a circle and a triangle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a tank? Try circle and square.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heroes fight on their own, you’re just there to make the decisions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/a2f755523ac4637058da945ad037f3e1.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies get weirder, stronger and ruder as you progress </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your Portal from swarming pests and brute squads </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn magical artifacts and upgrade your factory like there's no tomorrow.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/9179241185874b2c4309b589ce100cdd.poster.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/9179241185874b2c4309b589ce100cdd.webm?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/9179241185874b2c4309b589ce100cdd.mp4?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/ee75612b76ea8e50413b8cef9c2cd9a2.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different playable characters - ‘Masters’ - have different hero types and build strategies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with different characters to unlock their Arcane Knowledge (permanent upgrades) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a playstyle that suits you best </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/ce7ab3bf437060ea18bf204c1cf775e6.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=187 /></span>You can’t control your troops, but you can outsmart the darkness waiting to gobble up your kingdom, one conveyor belt at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world’s weirdest factory. You don’t swing swords or cast spells, instead you build tiny heroes out of shapes, and hope for the best as they come up against endless swarms of increasingly brutal enemies. All in a day’s work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/429a6aa911900a58e8a3cda41ca0ace9.poster.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/429a6aa911900a58e8a3cda41ca0ace9.webm?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/429a6aa911900a58e8a3cda41ca0ace9.mp4?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/cbd415d756e11bf8259348c631ac8f45.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=202 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop shapes onto conveyor belts to craft self-operation heroes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a soldier? Try a circle and a triangle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a tank? Try circle and square.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heroes fight on their own, you’re just there to make the decisions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/a2f755523ac4637058da945ad037f3e1.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies get weirder, stronger and ruder as you progress </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your Portal from swarming pests and brute squads </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn magical artifacts and upgrade your factory like there's no tomorrow.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/9179241185874b2c4309b589ce100cdd.poster.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/9179241185874b2c4309b589ce100cdd.webm?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/9179241185874b2c4309b589ce100cdd.mp4?t=1769665088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/ee75612b76ea8e50413b8cef9c2cd9a2.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different playable characters - ‘Masters’ - have different hero types and build strategies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with different characters to unlock their Arcane Knowledge (permanent upgrades) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a playstyle that suits you best </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389040/extras/ce7ab3bf437060ea18bf204c1cf775e6.avif?t=1769665088\" width=616 height=187 /></span>You can’t control your troops, but you can outsmart the darkness waiting to gobble up your kingdom, one conveyor belt at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
